      <h1> My Experience </h1>
      <ul>
	<li> This summer, I am the Media Analytics Intern at <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="http://www.mullenlowemediahub.com/">MullenLowe Mediahub</a>. </li>
	
	<li>This past spring I was a research assistant in the <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="http://www.indiana.edu/~cogdev/">Cognitive Development Lab</a> at Indiana University. I worked on a semester long research project that explored how children gain implicit and explicit knowledge about place values and how it relates to future mathematical achievement.</li>

	<li> Last summer, I was the Finance and Operations intern at <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.uplandbeer.com/">Upland Brewing Company</a>.There I focused on production margins throughout the supply chain, and wrote a comprehensive report summarizing my findings report using RMarkdown. </li>

	<li>This is my second semester as anm undergraduate teaching instructor for <a target="_blank" rel ="noopener noreferrer" href="https://registrar.indiana.edu/browser/soc4182/BIOL/BIOL-L111.shtml">BIOL-L 111:</a> Foundations of Biology: Diversity, Evolution, and Ecology. I really enjoyed the experience of teaching fellow students essential biology concepts.</li>
	
	<li>I am a former undergraduate research assistant in the <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://biology.indiana.edu/research/research-strengths/behavior/rosvall-lab.html">Rosvall Research Lab</a>. I helped assist with data collection on tree swallows nesting behavior, as well as maintain the RFID readers at the field sites.</li>
